{"tid":1741083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[雷射槍] 海關深水埗檢獲83枝懷疑不安全激光筆","createTime":"2019-11-20T07:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T07:43:48.000Z","uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e2276c36fe4d0ff558878d1b0ccb85a1f66a5177","tid":1741083,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:38:42.000Z","msg":"海關過去一周在深水埗7間零售店，檢取共83枝懷疑不安全激光筆，涉嫌違反《消費品安全條例》及其附屬法例。<br />\n<br />\n海關人員11月11日至15日期間在深水埗進行巡查及試購行動，發現7間零售店舖出售懷疑不安全激光筆。涉案激光筆分屬7款，當中一款沒有附上任何警告或警誡，另外6款則只附有英文使用警告或警誡。行動中，海關共檢取83枝懷疑不安全激光筆，將會送交化驗所作安全測試。調查仍在進行中。<br />\n<br />\n海關提醒市民，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>由於激光筆所發出的光束有機會損害眼睛和皮膚，在任何情況下都不應讓激光筆照射出的光點射向眼睛</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2308355/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2308355%2F&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLJS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=07343ace\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2308355/</a>"},{"pid":"aee1dd1abb3f0e1737c7e1912f72193ba8d9de89","tid":1741083,"uid":166506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:39:34.000Z","msg":"好撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437dd3b64e9fa56ca5ff33756ee089b23515bca6","tid":1741083,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:39:36.000Z","msg":"希望大家專心區選先<br />\n你而家出黎只會被捕 黑警拉你坐78 24號就投唔到票<br />\n到時區議會失守 政府就可以大大聲同外媒講市民企佢嗰邊<br />\n係同路人就一定會停一停抖一抖<br />\n邊個阻止區選進行就係鬼 因為客觀效果就係保皇得益<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">11月24日 血債票償 踢走保皇黨</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/250a150e3b7bce618995be275d28ff4e/5E448B03/t51.2885-15/sh0.08/e35/c180.0.1079.1079a/s640x640/70179621_135577684418097_5168140313520011975_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F250a150e3b7bce618995be275d28ff4e%2F5E448B03%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fsh0.08%2Fe35%2Fc180.0.1079.1079a%2Fs640x640%2F70179621_135577684418097_5168140313520011975_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D109&h=5380aa8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ebbd05607d64377652b38bad06cc25516cd60cc","tid":1741083,"uid":68598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:41:41.000Z","msg":"幾時去封哂所有工程野 殺到人嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3186a4f9f9997b522dd9e06cf0ccce9cfe8c2279","tid":1741083,"uid":110125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:43:48.000Z","msg":"豬肉刀都好危險 幾時冚哂啲肉檔"}]}